HEADWORD: Clitoris
<hw>Cli"to*ris</hw> <pr>(kl⟦imac⟧"t⟦osl⟧*r⟦icr⟧s <it>or</it>
kl⟦icr⟧t"⟦osl⟧*r⟦icr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr.
<grk>kleitori`s</grk>, fr. <grk>klei`ein</grk> to shut up. It is
